Floyd Mayweather looked nervous, Manny Pacquiao was happy
Sportsmail’s boxing correspondent Jeff Powell gives his latest update from Las Vegas as the mega-fight between Floyd Mayweather and Manny Pacquiao moves ever closer.
The weigh-in was held on Friday night in front of 12,000 fans at the MGM Grand in Las Vegas in what was itself a stunning event.
Both men came in under the welterweight limit and the fight is officially on.
